Package fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.factories

Class IMSolvingStrategyFactory

java.lang.Object
fr.lirmm.chocominer.app.specialized.factories.IMSolvingStrategyFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
SolvingStrategyFactory
public class IMSolvingStrategyFactory extends Object implements SolvingStrategyFactory
This factory allows for an efficient management of the different Itemset Mining SPMF strategies. It follows the Factory Pattern structure. For more information on its usefulness see this link.

      public FCISolvingStrategy createFCI(double minimumSupport, @Nullable String algorithmName)
      Instantiates a new FCI Solving Strategy.
      Parameters:
      minimumSupport - the minimum support an itemset X can have.
      algorithmName - the name of the algorithm that is to be used by the strategy, if not given, the strategy will choose its default algorithm.
      Returns:
      an FCI Solving strategy
